posts.title: **Deploying to Kubernetes Using CI/CD**
posts.descriptions: Kubernetes is a popular container orchestration platform that can be used to deploy and manage applications at scale. CI/CD, or Continuous Integration/Continuous Deployment, is a set of practices that automate the build, test, and deployment of software. By combining Kubernetes and CI/CD, you can automate the entire process of building, testing, and deploying your applications, which can save you time and money.
